scene.message:
Yukino: Whoa?!{nl}
O-outer space?! What is up{nl}
with this room???{waitkey}{clearbox}!?{nl}
Who are you...?{waitkey}{ret}

???: Um...{nl}
nice to meet you, everyone.{nl}
I'm "Kumi Hirose," entrusted{waitkey}with guarding this tower{waitkey}{clearbox}by the Snow Queen.{waitkey}{clearbox}Um... and so, I've been{nl}
ordered to kill you all,{nl}
but...{waitkey}{clearbox}...how about it?{nl}
I don't really feel like it,{waitkey}{clearbox}so why not surrender quietly{nl}
and live happily with us{nl}
in the dream world?{waitkey}{clearbox}...I'll at least spare{nl}
your lives?{waitkey}{ret}

Nanjo: What's this?{nl}
"I'm Kumi Hirose"?{waitkey}{clearbox}A girl like you, the guardian{nl}
of this tower?? Don't be{nl}
absurd. Don't make me laugh!{waitkey}{clearbox}You seem to be wearing{nl}
our school's uniform...{waitkey}{clearbox}Are you our student?{nl}
What year? If you're mocking{nl}
us with a bad joke,{nl}
I won't forgive it!{waitkey}{clearbox}Answer me! What are you{nl}
doing here?!{waitkey}{ret}

Brown: Hey hey hey...{nl}
she's wearing our uniform,{nl}
but who is she?{waitkey}{clearbox}A cute girl like you, the{nl}
boss here? Quit joking...{waitkey}Am I dreaming?{waitkey}{ret}

Ayase: What are you saying?!{nl}
This four-eyes!{nl}
Don't mess with us!{waitkey}{clearbox}A gloomy, super-weak-looking{nl}
girl like you couldn't be{nl}
the enemy boss!!{waitkey}{ret}

Kumi: Heeheehee...{nl}
I'd rather you didn't judge{nl}
people by looks alone...{waitkey}{clearbox}I'll kill you right now...{nl}
you little fools?{waitkey}{clearbox}It's always been this way...{nl}
No one ever tries to{nl}
listen to me!{waitkey}{clearbox}Humans really are just{nl}
a pack of fools...{waitkey}{clearbox}Enough. Vanish from{nl}
before me, would you.{waitkey}{ret}

Nanjo: Wh-?! This bloodlust!!{nl}
Don't tell me she's{nl}
really...!? Is she{nl}
going to... attack?{waitkey}{ret}

Elly: Oh... My...{nl}
What an ominous... aura...{nl}
Is she really...!?{waitkey}{clearbox}Everyone!{nl}
She's coming!!{waitkey}{ret}

Kumi: Heehee...{nl}
"Lord Hypnos"...{nl}
"Lord Hypnos"...{waitkey}{clearbox}...my prince...{nl}
"Lord Hypnos!"{nl}
Beat them down for me!{waitkey}{clearbox}They're the bad ones who{nl}
came to torment me!{waitkey}{ret}

Yukino: A-a Persona?!{waitkey}{clearbox}I see... so that's{nl}
how it is...{nl}
No holding back, everyone!{nl}
Here we go!{waitkey}{ret}

Yukino: ...Hmph!{nl}
This looks like the goal.{waitkey}{clearbox}That's right, isn't it?!{nl}
"Kumi Hirose," was it!{waitkey}{clearbox}Sorry to keep you waiting...{nl}
Now... we'll teach you{nl}
a lesson!{waitkey}{ret}

Kumi: So you finally{nl}
made it this far...{waitkey}{clearbox}Bound by the dull frame{nl}
of reality,{waitkey}{clearbox}not knowing - nor caring to{nl}
believe - that a paradise{nl}
called "dreams" exists{waitkey}in this world...{nl}
foolish people...!{waitkey}{ret}

Nanjo: And who's the fool...?!{nl}
You who've walked a life{nl}
knowing only how to run,{waitkey}{clearbox}then fled from the very act{nl}
of running itself -{nl}
you loser!{waitkey}{clearbox}There's nothing left to say!{nl}
Come at us!{waitkey}{ret}

Brown: Kumi-chan...{nl}
fighting a cute girl{nl}
like you...{waitkey}{clearbox}it pains me!{nl}
But it can't be helped...{waitkey}{clearbox}For the school!{waitkey}{clearbox}For justice!{waitkey}{clearbox}For my own glory!!{waitkey}{clearbox}Just go down already!{waitkey}{ret}

Ayase: Heh-heh!{nl}
A crammer like you!{waitkey}{clearbox}If the five of us Ayase{nl}
gang up on you, it's an{nl}
easy win!{waitkey}{clearbox}Apologize now while you can!{waitkey}{ret}

Kumi: Foolish people who{nl}
judge others by nothing{nl}
but appearances...{waitkey}{clearbox}"Lord Hypnos!"{waitkey}{clearbox}Help me!!{waitkey}{clearbox}Beat them down!!{waitkey}{ret}

Nanjo: What! That's...!?{nl}
The one from the{nl}
"Anti-Dream World"!{waitkey}{clearbox}Wasn't it just a product{nl}
of her dream?{waitkey}{ret}

Elly: It can't be!?{nl}
Kumi's... Persona!?{waitkey}{clearbox}The Hypnos in the Anti-Dream{nl}
World wasn't a product of{nl}
Kumi's dream after all!{waitkey}{ret}

Kumi: "Lord Hypnos!"{waitkey}{clearbox}Now, beat down those who{nl}
came even into my dream{nl}
to torment me!!{waitkey}{ret}
